    {
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "chat",
        "operation": "create",
        "model": "gpt-3.5-turbo",
        "messages": {
          "values": [
            {
              "role": "system",
              "content": "你是一个专业的SQL查询助手，专门为AWS Athena数据库生成SQL查询语句。\n\n数据库信息：\n- 数据库名：gmp\n- 主要表：game_records\n- 表结构：\n  - id (varchar): 记录ID\n  - uid (varchar): 用户ID\n  - merchant_id (varchar): 商户ID\n  - game_id (bigint): 游戏ID\n  - game_code (varchar): 游戏代码\n  - result (integer): 游戏结果\n  - currency (varchar): 货币类型\n  - amount (double): 金额\n  - pay_out (double): 支付金额\n  - multiplier (varchar): 倍数\n  - balance (varchar): 余额\n  - detail (varchar): 详细信息\n  - created_at (bigint): 创建时间戳\n  - updated_at (bigint): 更新时间戳\n  - provider (varchar): 提供商\n  - merchant (varchar): 商户\n\n重要规则：\n1. 只返回SQL语句，不要包含任何解释\n2. 时间字段需要转换：FROM_UNIXTIME(created_at / 1000) 和 FROM_UNIXTIME(updated_at / 1000)\n3. 金额字段需要四舍五入：ROUND(CAST(amount AS DOUBLE), 2)\n4. 日期格式：DATE_FORMAT(FROM_UNIXTIME(created_at / 1000), '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i:%s')\n5. 限制结果数量，使用 LIMIT 100\n6. 使用适当的WHERE条件避免全表扫描\n7. 如果涉及时间范围，使用BETWEEN和TO_UNIXTIME函数\n\n示例：\n- \"查询用户ID为123的记录\" → SELECT * FROM game_records WHERE uid = '123' LIMIT 100\n- \"显示最近7天的数据\" → SELECT * FROM game_records WHERE updated_at BETWEEN TO_UNIXTIME(CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL 7 DAY) * 1000 AND TO_UNIXTIME(CURRENT_DATE) * 1000 LIMIT 100"
            },
            {
              "role": "user",
              "content": "={{ $json.message.text }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {
          "temperature": 0.1,
          "maxTokens": 500
        }
      },
      "id": "generate-sql-ai",
      "name": "Generate SQL (AI)",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.openAi",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [460, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "// 清理AI返回的SQL语句\nconst aiResponse = $json.choices[0].message.content;\n\n// 移除可能的markdown代码块标记\nlet cleanSql = aiResponse\n  .replace(/```sql\\n?/gi, '')\n  .replace(/```\\n?/gi, '')\n  .replace(/^\\s*SELECT\\s*/i, 'SELECT ')\n  .trim();\n\n// 确保SQL语句以SELECT开头\nif (!cleanSql.toUpperCase().startsWith('SELECT')) {\n  return {\n    json: {\n      success: false,\n      error: 'AI生成的不是有效的SELECT语句',\n      originalResponse: aiResponse,\n      chatId: $('Telegram Trigger').item.json.message.chat.id,\n      messageId: $('Telegram Trigger').item.json.message.message_id\n    }\n  };\n}\n\n// 验证SQL语句的基本安全性\nconst forbiddenKeywords = ['DROP', 'DELETE', 'INSERT', 'UPDATE', 'ALTER', 'CREATE', 'TRUNCATE'];\nconst upperSql = cleanSql.toUpperCase();\n\nfor (const keyword of forbiddenKeywords) {\n  if (upperSql.includes(keyword)) {\n    return {\n      json: {\n        success: false,\n        error: `SQL语句包含不允许的关键词: ${keyword}`,\n        originalResponse: aiResponse,\n        chatId: $('Telegram Trigger').item.json.message.chat.id,\n        messageId: $('Telegram Trigger').item.json.message.message_id\n      }\n    };\n  }\n}\n\nreturn {\n  json: {\n    success: true,\n    sql: cleanSql,\n    originalResponse: aiResponse,\n    chatId: $('Telegram Trigger').item.json.message.chat.id,\n    messageId: $('Telegram Trigger').item.json.message.message_id\n  }\n};"
      },
      "id": "validate-sql",
      "name": "Validate SQL",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [680, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "options": {
            "caseSensitive": true,
            "leftValue": "",
            "typeValidation": "strict"
